room_title: Escape room "Private Eye" by Chronos Escape Room in Los Angeles
room_description: The year is 1943, the place New York City. Everywhere you go the city is bursting with life and excitement but beneath the glitz and glamour there are dark powers at play. You have been hired by Police Chief Donovan of the NYPD to investigate the whereabouts of a missing person, detective Frank Costigan. What you’ll find is anyone’s guess.
